Chordate/Otyebis Staff:



Chordate arrived outside of the Otyebis, four armed soldiers coming outside 
and escorting him inside.  After several minutes of walking through the 
Otyebis, one of the soldiers pointed to a door with his name above it.  He 
entered through it.
